      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg">Everything you need to know before we work together.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-6">

      <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">What industries do you work with?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600">All of them. We're deliberately industry-agnostic — wherever there's a workflow that can be improved with AI, we can help. We've focused on finance and legal in early conversations, but we work with businesses across healthcare, retail, HR, logistics, education, and more. <a href="/industries/" class="text-indigo-600 hover:underline">See our full list of industries.</a></p>
      </div>

      <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">What if I don't know exactly what I need?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600">That's exactly what the discovery call is for. Most clients come to us with a vague problem ("we're drowning in emails" or "we waste hours on reports"), not a specific solution. We ask the right questions, map your workflow, and identify where AI can make the most impact. You'll leave the call with a clear picture — even if you decide not to work with us.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">How long does a project take?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600">It depends entirely on scope. Simple automations can be live in a few days. A custom AI assistant with integrations into multiple tools might take 3–6 weeks. We always give you a clear timeline upfront, broken into milestones so you know exactly what to expect and when.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">How much does it cost?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Every project is scoped individually — we don't do one-size-fits-all pricing. We focus on volume and fair deals, so we're not priced like a big agency. After the free discovery call, we'll give you a detailed, transparent quote before anything starts. <a href="/pricing/" class="text-indigo-600 hover:underline">See how our pricing works.</a></p>
      </div>

      <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Do I need any technical expertise to work with you?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600">None at all. We handle everything — design, development, integration, testing, and deployment. Your job is to understand your business (which you already do); our job is to turn that into a working AI tool. We'll explain everything in plain language throughout the process.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Do you use existing AI tools or build from scratch?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Both — and we always recommend what's right for your specific situation. Sometimes the best solution is connecting existing tools (like OpenAI, Make, Zapier, or others) into a custom workflow. Sometimes we need to build something custom. We'll present options and explain the tradeoffs clearly.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">What happens after the project is delivered?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Every project includes 30 days of post-launch support to fix any issues and make sure everything runs smoothly. After that, you can continue with our Growth Partner retainer for ongoing iteration and support — or manage it independently. We'll make sure you know how everything works before we hand it off.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Is my business data safe?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Yes. We take data security seriously. We'll discuss data handling, privacy requirements, and any compliance needs during the discovery phase. We build tools that respect your data policies and, where required, work with privacy-preserving approaches to AI.</p>
      </div>

    </div>

